namespace pdg { /**

\fn pdg::Sprite::rotaryLimit

\brief limit the angle another sprite can have relative to this one (*Chipmunk Physics Only*)

If a breaking force is given, then the joint will break, generating a SpriteBreakEvent, if greater than that amount of rotational force (torque) is applied to the joint.

\returns the cpConstraint for the Joint in case you want to do anything special with it

**/ }